Program: Discovery
Title: American Association for the Advancement of Science
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwd6
Last Broadcast Date: 20 February 1995
Report from the annual AAAS's meeting featuring: New treatments for HIV and Aids: The Russian chemist, Dr Vil Mirzayanov, who revealed the existence of a Soviet chemical weapon programme: Happy doctors make better doctors: New fingerprint wavelet analysis. Presenter Roland Pease.